titles.title: A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard entered between October 2001 and September 2004.
A bill to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard entered between October 2001 and September 2004.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: Directs the Bureau of Customs and Border Protection to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to fiberboard.
